description: The fund is an actively managed exchange-traded fund ("ETF") that will invest, under normal circumstances at least 80% of the value of its net assets (plus the amount of any borrowings for investment purposes) in exchange-traded equity securities of U.S. large capitalization issuers that meet environmental, social, and governance ("ESG") standards, as determined by its sub-adviser. Its investment portfolio is focused, generally composed of at least 30 investment positions.
name: Stance Equity ESG Large Cap Core ETF
